{"tid":468540,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人想上教大SU","createTime":"2017-11-14T12:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T03:54:10.000Z","uid":53164,"like":26,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1f35a16c8ac3e70c2a7958b9bf17c7a9b50b41e7","tid":468540,"uid":53164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"呢個post希望可以召集到一班有心改善教大嘅人]<br />\n我明白而家教大嘅同學對中央莊有唔好嘅印象，覺得只係一班人小圈子圍爐，以為有少少權力就有優越感。所以我好想凝聚到一班有心嘅人，真正咁改善教大，亦都想可以令更加多人留意呢個社會發生緊咩事。<br />\n我明白上學生會責任大又好chur。但係我好想將SU份精神承傳落去，唔想染紅更唔想斷莊。自問我地目前搵到嘅莊員唔係個個能力好高，但大家都係真心想改善學生會形象同做到真正為學生發聲，唔係著眼喺私怨權鬥。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地都搵咗一段時間，試過揾身邊嘅人、係連登開post、係secret開post、甚至係c can揾人，無奈真係唔夠人。但未到最後一刻我地都唔會放棄，而你就係我嘅希望<br />\nthough hope is frail it's hard to kill<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTG: @Pusheen97"},{"pid":"fdde16c0946736482e7b1a022331e2cab022e276","tid":468540,"uid":53164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c75763d972faa6625b062735263d37b57616b3e","tid":468540,"uid":60883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf0963106b8daa1b2639cfc260fa94394e6ce42","tid":468540,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c60dfd19dab2a46efaa4cb69b4794e7e84f0e2","tid":468540,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:55:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"587e327f5a8fde321f4fe531ac129648dc522495","tid":468540,"uid":53164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/445772/page/4\" target=\